*This timeline starts with a snapshot of the project at 13/2/23 as Steve's starting date, anything completed before that date shows 1 days duration from that date. Scope & perspective is for 1st party camera & doorbell & 2x bypass box hardware and firmware Telus product management and associated dependencies to MVE1 only. Other teams & projects  only show key dependency intergration points (AWS API deliverables or sign-off & receving FXN prototypes. Note that this plan assumes FXN building the firmware and soft tooling for prototype builds.
